			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Aside from VotS (which I just got) and, of course, epic 1.0 (which I will probably have by the end of this week), are there any other great items for the &quot;non-uber&quot; bard that cannot be bought in the bazaar?  Stuff that can be soloed or perhaps done by a very small group of ubers?  I know shawl 8 is nice, but there are a lot more FT options now and I already did that with my enchanter, and don't really feel like doing it again.  I've looked at the guide section and didn't really see anything else that interesting.  Masks are way, WAY down on my priority list.  The only mask I'm remotely interested in is the halfling mask, mainly for shrink, but I think I'd almost rather camp the wand of imperceptibility than that.</span></td>
