				<td colspan="2"><span>I second the tiny cloak. I got it when I was 54 so I could start using it as soon as I dinged 55. I use it ALL THE TIME. It's only a 1.5 second cast, so it's great for invising up before going out for a pull or to pull mobs back without adds. I use it for running around invis in smallish stints too, like in WoS to get from ZI to a camp, or the same thing in BoT. I love my tiny cloak.</span></td>
